segmentosSRT.text:
Why don't you have a go?
Show them what it takes.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Business is good, Mr. Xie.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text:
Why don't you go home?
There'll be other times.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Your wife is right here.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text:
What's with you?
Can't take "no" for an answer?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: You want to make me lose face? Go away!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: I'll look after her for a few days?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Until you're set up elsewhere.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Want me to help you?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: A rare visitor indeed.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Master Fugui! It's been a year at least.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: I'm not one to lend money.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: I'll lend you something else. More practical.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: They are fabulous.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: My heart is full of sorrow
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: It's that hateful bandit, Jiang
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: I'm lucky to be alive
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: He gets compensation.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text:
Shall we invite him over?
Fengxia can check him out.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: He was very busy?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Dad, I saw Chunsheng yesterday.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: We have to draw a line between us and him.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: They say she's great. No problems.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: From the contractions, not right now.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12

segmentosSRT.text: Fengxia, don't be nervous.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_12
